[32m+[m[32m---[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m## Problem Statement Recap[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mBuild a **real-time misinformation detection agent** that:[m
[32m+[m[32m1. Monitors social media feeds for viral, harmful claims[m
[32m+[m[32m2. Cross-references claims against trusted national databases[m
[32m+[m[32m3. Generates structured fact-check reports (claim, evidence, citations, severity)[m
[32m+[m[32m4. Posts corrective, evidence-based responses when confidence + virality thresholds are met[m
[32m+[m[32m5. Logs every response with a confidence score for human audit/override[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m---[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m## Tech Stack (ML/AI Scope)[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m| Component | Technology |[m
[32m+[m[32m|---|---|[m
[32m+[m[32m| Agent Orchestration | **LangGraph** (multi-step agent with memory, tool nodes, rollback) |[m
[32m+[m[32m| LLM Backbone | **Claude claude-sonnet-4-20250514** (Anthropic SDK) |[m
[32m+[m[32m| NLP | **spaCy** + **sentence-transformers** (all-MiniLM-L6-v2) |[m
[32m+[m[32m| Vector Store | **Pinecone** (semantic dedup + claim similarity) |[m
[32m+[m[32m| Graph DB | **Neo4j AuraDB** (narrative/campaign detection) |[m
[32m+[m[32m| Amplification Model | **XGBoost** (virality/reach prediction) |[m
[32m+[m[32m| Translation | **Meta NLLB-200-distilled-600M** |[m
[32m+[m[32m| Multimodal | **Whisper** (audio transcription), **EasyOCR** (image text) |[m
[32m+[m[32m| External APIs | Google Fact Check Tools API, Tavily API, NewsAPI, WHO API |[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m---[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m## Step-by-Step Implementation Tasks[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m### Phase 1 — Foundation & Schema (H0–H6)[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m- [ ] **Task 1.1: Define `AgentState` TypedDict** (`agent/state.py`)[m
[32m+[m[32m  - Fields: `claim_id`, `original_text`, `translated_text`, `language`, `claims_extracted`, `evidence`, `verdict`, `risk_score`, `confidence`, `reasoning_chain`, `satire_flag`, `mutation_of`, `predicted_6h_reach`, `processed_at`[m
[32m+[m[32m  - This IS the contract shared with the Full-Stack Dev and Backend[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m- [ ] **Task 1.2: Create Verdict JSON Schema** (Pydantic model)[m
[32m+[m[32m  ```[m
[32m+[m[32m  { claim_id, label (FALSE|MISLEADING|UNVERIFIED|TRUE), confidence (0-1),[m
[32m+[m[32m    risk_score (0-1), reasoning_chain[], evidence_sources[{url, title,[m
[32m+[m[32m    credibility_score, excerpt}], satire_flag, language, mutation_of,[m
[32m+[m[32m    predicted_6h_reach, processed_at }[m
[32m+[m[32m  ```[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m- [ ] **Task 1.3: Build LangGraph skeleton** (`agent/graph.py`)[m
[32m+[m[32m  - Register all 9 node names (ingest → extract → translate → dedup → verify → score → guardrail → verdict → output)[m
[32m+[m[32m  - Define edges and conditional routing[m
[32m+[m[32m  - Empty node functions — fill logic node by node[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m- [ ] **Task 1.4: Write LLM prompts** (`prompts/`)[m
[32m+[m[32m  - `verdict_system.txt` — fact-checker system prompt (conservative: use UNVERIFIED if weak evidence)[m
[32m+[m[32m  - `claim_extract.txt` — atomic claim extraction prompt[m
[32m+[m[32m  - `red_team_system.txt` — adversarial variant generator prompt[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m- [ ] **Task 1.5: Set up `requirements.txt`**[m
[32m+[m[32m  - langgraph, anthropic, spacy, sentence-transformers, pinecone-client, neo4j, xgboost, langdetect, nllb (transformers), whisper, easyocr, httpx, aiokafka, etc.[m
