[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m### Phase 2 — NLP Extraction & Kafka Integration (H6–H14)[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m- [ ] **Task 2.1: Implement `ingest_node`** (`nodes/ingest.py`)[m
[32m+[m[32m  - Async Kafka consumer from `normalized_claims` topic[m
[32m+[m[32m  - Parse incoming message into `AgentState`[m
[32m+[m[32m  - Log with timestamp + topic + partition offset[m
[32m+[m
