[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m- [ ] **Task 3.1: Implement `verdict_node`** (`nodes/verdict.py`)[m
[32m+[m[32m  - Call Claude claude-sonnet-4-20250514 via Anthropic SDK with `verdict_system.txt` prompt[m
[32m+[m[32m  - Input: claim text + all gathered evidence[m
[32m+[m[32m  - Output: structured JSON matching verdict schema[m
